bench = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "dice-combat"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc_macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2018"
required_features = []

[package]
name = "dice-combat"
edition = "2018"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = ["Rob Williams <robwilliams42@gmail.com>"]
keywords = []
categories = []
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true
publish = true

[dependencies]
quad-rand = "0.1.1"
rmp-serde = "0.14.4"
serde_json = "1.0.59"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.117"
features = ["derive"]
optional = false

[dependencies.specs]
version = "0.16.1"
features = ["specs-derive"]
optional = false
default-features = false

[dependencies.ws]
version = "0.9.1"
features = []
optional = false
[profile.dev]
